## Africana Studies Relation  

The Schomburg Center is a cornerstone of **Africana Studies**, providing primary source materials that document the struggles, triumphs, and cultural expressions of people of African descent. Its resources help scholars and activists understand the complexity and richness of Black experiences across the globe.  

